Title: Blue Heart - European Charm Bracelet Style - Love - Murano Floral Beads!
Description: Kensari Bracelet Authentic - Kensari Bracelet - Blue Heart Floral Murano Beads & Heart Charm ( Comes With Velveteen Storage Pouch! ) Kensari Bracelets are handmade by me and crafted for quality. The materials I use are personally selected by me and include but not limited to: ( Bracelets ) Gold or Silver Plated ~ ( Charms ) Gold or Silver Plated and/or Tibetan Gold or Silver ~ ( Beads ) Porcelain - Resin - Acrylic and/or Acrylic Pearls - Murano and Millefiori and other quality glass name brands - Stardust glitter spacer beads - Gold or Silver Plated and/or Tibetan Gold or Silver spacer beads - ( Rhinestone/Crystal ) Some Swarovsky - All picked for their quality and shimmer! Size: See measure ruler photo in our listing photos above. Also has a 2" extension chain. Beads & Charms can be added or removed by unscrewing the end of the bracelet. Please Note: The photo does not show actual size, please refer to Description for size details. Color may very slightly due to the color calibration of each individual monitor. Remember to measure your wrist and allow 1/2 to 1 inch longer to leave room for the beads. To Clean your bracelet: Rub lightly with a soft cloth. Store in a sealed plastic bag when not in use to keep the air out. Never use Jewelry Cleaner of any kind, it will remove the finish on your bracelet, beads and charms. PAYMENT: We accept PAYPAL only. Please Note: Payment should be completed at end of auction. Shipping: We ship to the Continental United States Only! RETURNS: No returns on handmade jewelry.
